arts.ttl: AZ Alkmaar knock Manchester United out the UEFA Youth League
arts.sum: AZ Alkmaar’s U19 side have progressed to the next round of the UEFA Youth League after a 0-0 draw at Manchester United on Tuesday. AZ progresses 2-1 on aggregate. After a 2-1 win in the first leg in Alkmaar, AZ went into the game with Jayden Addai in their starting eleven.
